:<font size="15">סבב</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
סבב / sâbab / saw-bab'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''סבב'''

# To [[revolve]], surround or border; used in various applications, literally and figuratively: - bring, cast, fetch, lead, make, walk, X whirl, X round about, be about on every side, apply, avoid, beset (about), besiege, bring again, carry (about), change, cause to come about, X circuit, (fetch a) compass (about, round), drive, environ, X on every side, beset (close, come, compass, go, stand) round about, remove, return, set, sit down, turn (self) (about, aside, away, back).

